---
import Layout from '../layouts/main.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Public Code US - Our Mission"
	description="Learn about the Public Code US campaign, our mission, and how you can get involved in demanding transparency in government software."
	currentPage="/about"
>
	{/* Hero */}
	<section class="bg-nb-purple text-nb-light border-b-4 border-nb-dark py-20">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
			<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black uppercase italic mb-6">About Us</h1>
			<p class="text-lg font-bold">
				We're a movement of developers, activists, and citizens demanding that government software should be publicly owned and transparent.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	{/* Mission */}
	<section class="bg-nb-light border-b-4 border-nb-dark py-20">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
			<h2 class="text-4xl font-black uppercase italic text-nb-dark mb-8">Our Mission</h2>
			<div class="space-y-6">
				<div class="border-4 border-nb-dark bg-nb-cyan p-8">
					<p class="font-bold text-nb-dark text-lg leading-relaxed">
						To ensure that software developed with public money in the United States is made openly available as Free and Open Source Software. We believe government software should be:
					</p>
				</div>

				<ul class="space-y-4 text-lg font-bold text-nb-dark">
					<li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
						<span class="text-3xl">🔓</span>
						<span><strong>Open:</strong> Citizens can inspect the code that governs public services.</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
						<span class="text-3xl">🛡️</span>
						<span><strong>Secure:</strong> Thousands of independent developers can audit and improve security.</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
						<span class="text-3xl">💰</span>
						<span><strong>Efficient:</strong> Reusable across agencies, saving taxpayers billions.</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
						<span class="text-3xl">🚀</span>
						<span><strong>Innovative:</strong> Public code attracts developers and entrepreneurs.</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	{/* Why Now */}
	<section class="bg-nb-yellow border-b-4 border-nb-dark py-20">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
			<h2 class="text-4xl font-black uppercase italic text-nb-dark mb-8">Why Now?</h2>
			<div class="space-y-6">
				<div class="card-nb bg-nb-dark text-nb-light">
					<p class="font-bold text-lg">
						The pandemic exposed critical gaps in government technology. States spent billions building incompatible unemployment systems. Schools couldn't coordinate online learning. Agencies duplicated work instead of sharing solutions.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="card-nb bg-nb-light border-4 border-nb-dark">
					<p class="font-bold text-nb-dark text-lg">
						Europe is leading. Italy, France, and the EU are passing laws requiring public code. The rest of the world is watching. America can't fall behind on this.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="card-nb bg-nb-pink text-nb-dark">
					<p class="font-bold text-lg">
						Citizens are demanding change. From election security to vaccine distribution, people know government software is broken. This is the moment to fix it.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	{/* How to Get Involved */}
	<section class="bg-nb-light border-b-4 border-nb-dark py-20">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
			<h2 class="text-4xl font-black uppercase italic text-nb-dark mb-12">How to Get Involved</h2>
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
				<div class="card-nb">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase italic text-nb-dark mb-4">Sign the Petition</h3>
					<p class="font-bold text-nb-dark mb-6">
						Add your signature to show support. Every signature strengthens our hand with policymakers.
					</p>
					<a href="/sign" class="btn-nb btn-nb-primary">
						Go Sign Now
					</a>
				</div>

				<div class="card-nb">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase italic text-nb-dark mb-4">Share & Advocate</h3>
					<p class="font-bold text-nb-dark mb-6">
						Talk to your friends, family, and colleagues. Share on social media. Contact your representatives.
					</p>
					<a href="/resources" class="btn-nb">
						Get Sharing Materials
					</a>
				</div>

				<div class="card-nb">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase italic text-nb-dark mb-4">Volunteer</h3>
					<p class="font-bold text-nb-dark mb-6">
						Help organize ballot initiatives in your state. Work on campaigns. Build the movement.
					</p>
					<a href="mailto:hello@publiccodeus.org" class="btn-nb">
						Get Involved
					</a>
				</div>

				<div class="card-nb">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase italic text-nb-dark mb-4">Donate</h3>
					<p class="font-bold text-nb-dark mb-6">
						Fund ballot initiatives and campaigns. Support the movement financially.
					</p>
					<button class="btn-nb btn-nb-yellow" disabled>
						Coming Soon
					</button>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	{/* Contact */}
	<section class="bg-nb-cyan border-b-4 border-nb-dark py-20">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
			<h2 class="text-4xl font-black uppercase italic text-nb-dark mb-8">Get in Touch</h2>
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
				<div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-black uppercase italic text-nb-dark mb-4">Contact Information</h3>
					<div class="space-y-4 font-bold text-nb-dark">
						<p>
							<strong>Email:</strong><br />
							<a href="mailto:hello@publiccodeus.org" class="text-nb-pink hover:underline">hello@publiccodeus.org</a>
						</p>
						<p>
							<strong>Threads:</strong><br />
							<a href="https://threads.net/@publiccodeus" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-nb-pink hover:underline">@publiccodeus</a>
						</p>
						<p>
							<strong>GitHub:</strong><br />
							<a href="https://github.com/publiccodeus" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-nb-pink hover:underline">github.com/publiccodeus</a>
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-black uppercase italic text-nb-dark mb-4">Partners & Allies</h3>
					<p class="font-bold text-nb-dark mb-4">
						We work alongside:
					</p>
					<ul class="font-bold text-nb-dark text-sm space-y-2">
						<li>✓ Free Software Foundation Europe (FSFE)</li>
						<li>✓ Linux Foundation</li>
						<li>✓ Electronic Frontier Foundation (EFF)</li>
						<li>✓ Open Source Initiative (OSI)</li>
						<li>✓ Local tech communities & open source projects</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	{/* CTA */}
	<section class="bg-nb-dark text-nb-light border-b-4 border-nb-dark py-16">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black uppercase italic mb-6">Join the Movement</h2>
			<a href="/sign" class="btn-nb btn-nb-pink inline-block">
				Sign the Petition
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
